Title: Back to Earth (Part Two)
Writer: Rob Grant (creator), Doug Naylor (creator), Doug Naylor
Actors: Chris Barrie, Craig Charles, Danny John-Jules, Robert Llewellyn
Plot: Rimmer's replacement, Katerina, is determined to guide Lister back to his home planet. But Earth in 2009 is not everything the boys had expected, and Rimmer has no intention of being replaced.
